art_image_1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-48081"/></figure><p></p><p> ANYCOLOR于2月5日宣布，由于“ <em><a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多次违反合同以及在SNS上进行误导性和虚假的陈述和行为</a></em>”，它已终止与Seren Ryugetsu的合同。此外，该公司还受到海外VTuber观众和粉丝的激烈批评，其中<a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">IR公告称<em>“对业绩的影响极小</em>”。</a></p><p>自2月13日Elira Pendora频道播出以及ANYCOLOR社长<strong>拓野陆久</strong>发表声明视频后，《NIJISANJI EN》（新）订阅人数的减少似乎再次加速。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="yzKOC4viQv"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolors-ceo-tazumi-riku-released-statement-in-response-to-furious-criticism-of-the-company/">ANYCOLOR 总裁卓野陆 (Riku Takuno) 发表声明，回应对该公司的激烈批评。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR 总裁 Riku Takuno 发表声明，回应对该公司的激烈批评” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolors-ceo-tazumi-riku-released-statement-in-response-to-furious-criticism-of-the-company/embed/#?secret=JnWog5UFyx#?secret=yzKOC4viQv" data-secret="yzKOC4viQv" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="dReAY2IPzY"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-elira-pendora-expressed-criticized-selen-tatsuki-and-support-for-anycolor/">NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Elira Pendora批评Seren Ryugetsu并表示支持ANYCOLOR</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Elira Pendora批评Seren Ryugetsu并表示支持ANYCOLOR” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-elira-pendora-expressed-criticized-selen-tatsuki-and-support-for-anycolor/embed/#?secret=67uiKXtCN3#?secret=dReAY2IPzY" data-secret="dReAY2IPzY" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>另一方面，据称是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声优模特的VTuber <strong>Dokibird</strong>的订阅人数自2月5日起迅速增加，截至2月13日21点16分已达到50万。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="HxwDKJppgc"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-dokibird-reached-youtube-subscribers-500k/">VTuber Dokibird 拥有 50 万订阅者，据说是前 Seren Ryugetsu</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Dokibird 订阅者数量达到 50 万” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-dokibird-reached-youtube-subscribers-500k/embed/#?secret=rgDqiNYmP5#?secret=HxwDKJppgc" data-secret="HxwDKJppgc" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p>此次NIJISANJI EN（新）注册人才数量的大幅减少被认为在VTuber行业中是史无前例的。可以毫不夸张地说，目前ANYCOLOR和二十三寺园（新）所带来的局面，是一场彻底失去观众和粉丝信任、彻底崩溃的危机。被认为是将该人置于某种特定的情境中。 </p><p></p><div class="rwcjo65cc8ad042413" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
